Text: 'Hi This Is Naseer Rind From Quetta Balochistan Pakistan .I am a traveling filmmaker
  working for a long time in backward area whee we don''t have any leaning academy
  of school. I want to explore my Country and my Provinces and international tours.Film
  is my Passion and Profession .Through This fellow ship I will lean a lot to explore
  my dreams .

  Through This trip I will Capture different cultures Food,Dance,Traditional  Videos
  and also a good opportunity to meet new filmmakers for communication.'
